{"tid":676954,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"打句show blocked user出黎係咪威D","createTime":"2018-05-24T19:38:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-30T19:24:57.000Z","uid":181819,"like":8,"dislike":113,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"8d05a214a143eca593f3827fd314728f50dc5c26","tid":676954,"uid":181819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T19:38:39.000Z","msg":"　<br />\n<br />\n掩耳盜鈴<br />\n<br />\n釋義：比喻自己欺騙自己。<br />\n<br />\n故事：傳說有一個人想把人家的大鐘偷走，可是這鐘太大，怎樣也搬不走。<br />\n<br />\n他便找來一個錘子，希望把鐘砸碎，再一塊一塊地運走。但他用錘子一<br />\n<br />\n敲，鐘就響了起來。他怕人家知他偷東西，便趕忙用手掩住耳朵，以為<br />\n<br />\n自己聽不到鐘聲，別人也不會聽見。(見《呂氏春秋．自知》)<br />\n<br />\n例句：這項計劃錯漏百出已是人人皆知的事，你又何必「掩耳盜鈴」，把計<br />\n<br />\n劃說得那麼完美。<br />\n<br />\n近義：自欺欺人/掩目捕雀<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdd9e5f31392a9a2f3c6331d332b5981ebcbcb35","tid":676954,"uid":181819,"like":5,"dislike":38,"score":-33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T19:45:37.000Z","msg":"一唔鍾意就block，最後發現單機個個係自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47d39f7049b60899ac127e82a5d0255dbe31c079","tid":676954,"uid":181819,"like":1,"dislike":30,"score":-29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T19:54:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一唔鍾意就block，最後發現單機個個係自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"02598521e556a5a70a39407849bcf8bcb62ed8e2","tid":676954,"uid":181819,"like":1,"dislike":26,"score":-25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T20:00:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一唔鍾意就